#BharatBiotech Covid vaccine volunteer died of suspected poisoning: Bharat Biotech.

Deepak Marawi,42, who had taken part in the trial of Covaxin, the indigenous coronavirus vaccine developed by Bharat Biotech, died nine days later in Bhopal.
